These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, soy-milk, 7up, sprite
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, russian, spanish, turkish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, zinnia, rose, daffodil
City: edinburgh, miami, hannover, liverpool
 1. the colombian is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
 2. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is the russian##1
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hannover##5
 6. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to miami##5
 7. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
 8. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the spanish##3
10. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person drinking lemonade##7
11. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
12. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##5
13. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | sprite    | soy-milk | 7up    | lemonade   |
| Nationality   | colombian | spanish | russian | turkish |
| Flower           | zinnia       | rose   | daffodil  | daisy     |
| City     | edinburgh      | hannover   | liverpool    | miami    |

