.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
House: victorian, townhouse, tower, craftsman
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, thriller, time-travel
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, august, april, january
4 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, rat, horse
 1. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
 4. the owner of the rat is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5
 7. the craftsman house is somewhere between the owner of the goldfish and the person who's birthday is in may##7
 8. the victorian house is in an odd position##4
 9. the victorian house is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
10. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
11. the person who's birthday is in august is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| House          | victorian   | tower       | craftsman    | townhouse      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | time-travel | crime         | thriller   |
| Birthday   | january   | may  | august       | april |
| Pet         | dog      | rat  | horse | goldfish |

