 7. the project-manager is not the person who growssunflower##6
 8. the person who growstulip is not the social-worker##6
 9. the bartender is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
10. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
11. the designer is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who likes mauve##1

