 1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6
 5. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
 7. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the person driving the roller is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the trike##7
10. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
11. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's sport is climbing##1
12. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's hobby is video-games##7
13. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3

