.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Food         | zucchini      | blueberry   | cranberry   | spinach       |
| Beverage   | tea | hot-chocolate    | sprite | water       |
| Color   | blood-red  | mauve | blue   | purple     |
| Sport         | baseball   | soccer    | rowing   | skateboarding |

