.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, mirinda, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, animation, adventure, spy
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, nigerian, chinese, spanish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, bellflower, amaryllis, daffodil
 1. the spanish is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 3. the spanish is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growsamaryllis##2
 4. the italian is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 5. the person watching animation movies is not the person who growsbellflower##6
 6. the spanish is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person watching spy movies##7
 8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
 9. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
10. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the spanish##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is the person watching adventure movies##1
12. the person watching adventure movies is not the person who growsamaryllis##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk   | tea     | mirinda   | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre       | spy   | martial-arts | animation | adventure    |
| Nationality      | chinese | spanish | italian   | nigerian  |
| Flower        | daffodil | azalea     | amaryllis   | bellflower |

