.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, nigerian, dutch, indonesian
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, chess, filmmaking
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, game, blend, bongani
There 4 different types of food: lime, apricot, pineapple, potato
 1. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5
 2. the person eating lime is between the person who's hobby is chess and the prince-smoker##2
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 4. the dutch is on the far right##1
 5. the bongani-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person eating apricot is not the blend-smoker##6
 7. the blend-smoker is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
 8. the person eating lime is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
 9. the bongani-smoker is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
10. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
11. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person eating potato##1
12. the person who's hobby is chess is not the nigerian##6
13. the blend-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
14. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
15. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the indonesian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Nationality      | nigerian      | spanish        | indonesian          | dutch    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | camping    | chess          | board-games |
| Cigar           | prince  | game   | blend | bongani      |
| Food   | potato       | lime | pineapple          | apricot        |

