.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
House: wooden, victorian, cape-cod, ranch-style
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, boat, bus, trike
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, satire, thriller, sports
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 2. the person driving the bus is the cape-cod house##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is the person watching sports movies##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is between the ranch-style house and the victorian house##2
 5. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
 6. the person watching musical movies is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the wooden house##7
 7. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
 8. the person watching musical movies is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
10. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
12. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| House   | ranch-style      | cape-cod     | victorian   | wooden    |
| Transport     | trike | bus   | boat | subway |
| Movie-Genre     | sports        | thriller     | musical  | satire      |
| Sport   | rowing       | water-polo | cricket   | skiing    |

 